snippet.title: Hannah - Launch Trailer | Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X
snippet.description:
Hannah is available now for Steam, Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S!

Hannah is set in a surreal retro world where memories and fears multiply and mix each other in fascinating ways. You'll be able to climb ropes, swing, slide, solve puzzles, assemble gadgets and vehicles, as well as being able to use enemies to go unnoticed.

Xbox: https://tinyurl.com/hannahxbox
Steam: https://tinyurl.com/Hannahsteam

Follow us on social media:
 https://twitter.com/qubytegames
https://www.instagram.com/qubyteinteractive/
https://discord.gg/qubyte
___________________________________________________________________________

About QUByte Interactive
QUByte is the largest console game developer and publisher in Latin America. Our goal is to develop the industry through leading game portability and publishing partnerships, which we previously classified as limited in scope, to all available platforms.

About Spaceboy
SpaceBoy is a creative studio formed by multidisciplinary artists focused on creating mesmerizing audiovisual content; hand in hand with the development of stories, processes and personalized techniques.
